{"tid":781552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美食博覽2018】龍蝦姐重出江湖！用1元贏26盒鮑魚　求網民放過","createTime":"2018-08-16T03:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T04:13:35.000Z","uid":32938,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f205836a521d82bebf2259de47c8b40f0001e5","tid":781552,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1755016/org/d97d3f2d88c6d9a447d3de806b9ee1a1.jpg/DlCn2JLLVutxDVDaxgemm1Y2yZmJVCVrpVjoQqVY6EI?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1755016%2Forg%2Fd97d3f2d88c6d9a447d3de806b9ee1a1.jpg%2FDlCn2JLLVutxDVDaxgemm1Y2yZmJVCVrpVjoQqVY6EI%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=89f5c48e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美食博覽2018今日（16日）開鑼，不少市民一早前來排隊。排頭位人士早於周二（14日）上午前來，以「1蚊皇鮑車」為目標，期望買得「盤滿缽滿」。美食博覽常客「龍蝦姐」今年再度登場，並以1元贏得26盒鮑魚禮盒，歡喜背後她向記者大吐苦水，希望網民能夠放過她：「我真係畀你哋害得好慘！」贏得鮑魚的她，原本跟隊員一同望着記者拍照，但擔心被人認出，左閃右避。<br />\n<br />\n2014年冬日美食節玩夾龍蝦遊戲時，一句「你個嘢壞咗呀」，被網民認識並傳頌至今的「龍蝦姐」，今年再度重出江湖。今年她轉玩搶鮑魚，為在美食博覽搶購心頭好，「龍蝦姐」在會展場外排隊等候二日，最終成功跟4名隊友贏得1元26盒鮑魚。<br />\n<br />\n當「龍蝦姐」得知獲勝後，一度歡喜得開懷大笑，惟發現被傳媒認出後，態度突變，更大吐苦水，希望網民能夠放過她：「我真係畀你哋害得好慘！」大合照後，她一度走到遠處，著職員為她包妥禮盒，並在購入其他海味產品後，悄悄離開，可惜由於戰利品太重，未能拖走，最後由記者協助再度組裝，才能離去。"},{"pid":"1eece8c2c6c0f86126d91bc2edea85170601d982","tid":781552,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後由記者協助再度組裝</blockquote><br />\n點解記者會做啲咁嘅嘢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a687d24a194ef2f68b654d578a4bc5b2f1482d00","tid":781552,"uid":36321,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"1eece8c2c6c0f86126d91bc2edea85170601d982","tid":781552,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後由記者協助再度組裝</blockquote><br />\n點解記者會做啲咁嘅嘢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"純粹幫下人啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65011b0a1a06ba9fa8b96fb86edfebca3d50156f","tid":781552,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"「龍蝦姐」在會展場外排隊等候二日，最終成功跟4名隊友贏得1元26盒鮑魚。"},{"pid":"ca52835fda518a9241f5c460389ff2c3dce8e0a0","tid":781552,"uid":130143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbbd7e0c2e8fe025e26319c66b8fe1f6a10329b","tid":781552,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你</span></span>"},{"pid":"d69cdceb3642fa649c94b4f7fad5436604d7a3ec","tid":781552,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"你個嘢壞左呀"},{"pid":"21a5bea48fc8ae53fa2690b4c970a077c88ac216","tid":781552,"uid":63950,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:41:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ebbea6723c4d90b2c88959b55b607ba57e0cd72","tid":781552,"uid":40903,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:01:40.000Z","msg":"咁撚無恥既野都做得出 預左啦下嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e8af95dfb9ab4892f5a9edf94f0b8370cc3b47","tid":781552,"uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"又踩港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地用2日時間排隊<br />\n1蚊贏26盒係耐性恆心嘅表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜野叫貪少便宜，你地唔抵得就話人貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cd837b2e1ee5a55acd02d25701434d96a1d620","tid":781552,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:06:52.000Z","msg"